headline: Danaher Announces Diagnostic Development and Commercialization Partnership to Scale Precision Medicine
summary: Danaher Corporation (NYSE: DHR) ("Danaher"), a global science and technology innovator, announced today the launch of a partnership with AstraZeneca (LSE/STO/Nasdaq: AZN) to develop and commercialize novel diagnostic tools and tests intended to help clinicians better determine which patients would most benefit from precision medicine treatments.
